song.title: Keyz to New Junk City
song.info:
From [url=http://www.mazedude.com/aa/]The American Album[/url]
Track # 6 from my epic "American Album" remix project. A fun and synthy arrangement of the New Junk City theme from Earthworm Jim, done in an exploration of the "Keyz to the City" samplepack, complete with my own Mazedude goodness, and even some scat singing by Amanda Lea.
Original theme by Tommy Tallarico.
